rows.label: qev055202_MSG0001
rows.name:
We Orphe used smoke to alert each other to danger
back when we were the Ganglion's captives.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055202_MSG0002
rows.name:
I never expected it to be used in this manner,
but one does what one must.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055202_MSG0004
rows.name:
He has suffered mild exhaustion, but is anticipated to
recover quickly. There should be no cause for worry.[ST:wait ]
